1:42:03.149 --> 1:42:06.722
is that... makes us believe
that Ronald Reagan will win

1:42:06.757 --> 1:42:09.890
a very substantial
victory tonight.

1:42:09.925 --> 1:42:11.364
-Very substantial.
-Oh... -Oh, my...

1:42:11.399 --> 1:42:12.893
What have we come to?

1:42:12.928 --> 1:42:14.400
IRVING:
Morons.

1:42:14.435 --> 1:42:16.666
Morons from sea to shining sea.

