1:44:29.064 --> 1:44:30.668
First of all...

1:44:32.232 --> 1:44:34.199
Happy Thanksgiving.

1:44:35.169 --> 1:44:37.840
This is a wonderful
tradition we have.

1:44:37.875 --> 1:44:41.382
That our family has sponsored
over the years.

1:44:41.417 --> 1:44:42.878
Uh...

1:44:42.913 --> 1:44:47.685
the annual Forest Manor
Thanksgiving Dance.

1:44:47.720 --> 1:44:50.490
It's a chance to come together,

1:44:50.525 --> 1:44:53.559
be grateful for all
we've been given

1:44:53.594 --> 1:44:56.991
and all the positive things
in life.

1:44:57.763 --> 1:44:59.961
Personally, when I look out

1:44:59.996 --> 1:45:04.702
and I see all these
beautiful kids,

1:45:04.737 --> 1:45:07.474
you're ready to face the world.

1:45:07.509 --> 1:45:10.576
But it's not all fun and games.

1:45:10.611 --> 1:45:13.909
Because you have an obligation
to be the leaders

1:45:13.944 --> 1:45:17.913
