in finance, politics,

1:45:17.948 --> 1:45:21.389
to be CEOs and senators
and presidents.

1:45:21.424 --> 1:45:23.050
You are the elite.

1:45:23.085 --> 1:45:24.920
("Justice Tonight/Kick It Over"
by The Clash playing)

1:45:24.955 --> 1:45:27.758
I couldn't have more hope
than I do

1:45:27.793 --> 1:45:30.090
at this very moment
in our future.

1:45:30.125 --> 1:45:32.730
